---
title: Maple-Mustard Grilled Chicken with Apple Slaw and Buttery Potatoes
description: Canadiana, on the grill! We've filled this summer supper with Canadian flavours, from maple, to mustard and apples, this one's got it all.  Comforting buttery potatoes and refreshing apple slaw complete this backyard beauty.
